---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SiteFooter from '../components/SiteFooter.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — Side Quests To Freedom"
  description="Learn about Side Quests To Freedom — a resource for anyone building financial freedom through side hustles and online income."
  canonicalUrl="https://sidequeststofreedom.com/about"
>
  <div class="bg-grid" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="bg-orb bg-orb-1" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="bg-orb bg-orb-2" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <main class="container page-container">
    <nav class="breadcrumb">
      <a href="/links" class="breadcrumb-link">Home</a>
      <span aria-hidden="true">›</span>
      <span>About</span>
    </nav>

    <article class="prose-page">
      <h1>About Side Quests To Freedom</h1>

      <p class="lead">
        Side Quests To Freedom is a personal finance and side hustle resource dedicated to helping
        everyday people build real, sustainable income outside their 9-to-5.
      </p>

      <h2>What This Site Is About</h2>
      <p>
        Financial freedom doesn't have to mean retiring at 30 or going viral overnight. For most
        people, it starts with a side quest — a small, deliberate action taken alongside ordinary
        life to build income, skills, and options over time.
      </p>
      <p>
        This site covers the strategies, tools, and mindset shifts that make that possible:
        freelancing, content creation, passive income streams, digital products, and more. No
        get-rich-quick promises — just honest, tested approaches and the occasional reality check.
      </p>

      <h2>Who Runs This</h2>
      <p>
        Side Quests To Freedom is run by a solo creator who has spent years experimenting with side
        hustles — some successful, some spectacular failures — and documenting what actually works.
        The goal is to share real experience rather than recycled advice, so you spend less time
        wading through noise and more time making progress.
      </p>

      <h2>What You'll Find Here</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>In-depth guides on starting and scaling specific side hustles</li>
        <li>Honest reviews of platforms, tools, and services</li>
        <li>Income reports and case studies grounded in real data</li>
        <li>Actionable strategies for managing your time and money while building a side income</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>A Note on Affiliate Links</h2>
      <p>
        Some posts on this site contain affiliate links. If you purchase through one of these links,
        I may earn a small commission at no extra cost to you. I only recommend products and
        services I've used or thoroughly researched. See the full <a href="/disclaimer">Disclaimer</a>
        for details.
      </p>

      <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
      <p>
        Questions, feedback, or collaboration inquiries are always welcome. Head over to the
        <a href="/contact">Contact page</a> to reach out.
      </p>
    </article>

    <SiteFooter />
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-container {
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .breadcrumb {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: rgba(var(--text-rgb), 0.35);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .breadcrumb-link {
    color: rgba(var(--purple-rgb), 0.6);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .breadcrumb-link:hover {
    color: var(--purple);
  }

  .prose-page h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: rgba(var(--text-rgb), 0.75);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(var(--text-rgb), 0.07);
  }

  .prose-page h2 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .prose-page p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: rgba(var(--text-rgb), 0.75);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
  }

  .prose-page ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
  }

  .prose-page li {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: rgba(var(--text-rgb), 0.75);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .prose-page a {
    color: var(--purple);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .prose-page a:hover {
    color: var(--green);
  }
</style>
